    <item>
      <title>SSH into EC2 instance with instance ID</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015-11-30-ssh-into-ec2-instance-with-instance-id/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Nov 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015-11-30-ssh-into-ec2-instance-with-instance-id/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Make sure you&amp;rsquo;ve installed and configured the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/aws/aws-cli&#34;&gt;aws-cli&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/stedolan/jq&#34;&gt;jq&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Drop this function into your .zshrc or .bashrc:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#cf222e&#34;&gt;function&lt;/span&gt; ec2-ssh &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;  ssh &lt;span style=&#34;color:#cf222e&#34;&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;aws ec2 describe-instances --filter &lt;span style=&#34;color:#953800&#34;&gt;Name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;instance-id,Values&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#953800&#34;&gt;$1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; jq &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;.Reservations[0].Instances[0].PrivateIpAddress&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#1f2328&#34;&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; tr -d &lt;span style=&#34;color:#0a3069&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;#34;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#cf222e&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#0550ae&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And now you can ssh into your EC2 instance:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;background-color:#fff;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ ec2-ssh i-6g5c7ed4&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Outbound connections from Docker with VirtualBox not working?</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015-11-17-outbound-connections-from-docker-with-virtualbox-not-working/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Nov 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015-11-17-outbound-connections-from-docker-with-virtualbox-not-working/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Using Docker and VirtualBox and having trouble making outbound&#xA;connections? You may have errors similar to:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;curl: (7) Failed connect to 10.0.2.224:8000; No route to host&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;Error: Redis connection to redis:6379 failed - connect EHOSTUNREACH&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s what I did to fix it:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I ssh&amp;rsquo;d into the Docker machine:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$ docker-machine ssh dev&#xA;```&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Checked eth0&amp;rsquo;s subnet:&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;$ ifconfig eth0&#xA;eth0      Link encap:Ethernet  HWaddr 08:00:27:C8:C7:50&#xA;inet addr:10.254.0.15  Bcast:10.254.0.255  Mask:255.255.255.0&#xA;inet6 addr: fe80::a00:27ff:fec8:c750/64 Scope:Link&#xA;UP BROADCAST RUNNING MULTICAST  MTU:1500  Metric:1&#xA;RX packets:230796 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 frame:0&#xA;TX packets:62400 errors:0 dropped:0 overruns:0 carrier:0&#xA;collisions:0 txqueuelen:1000&#xA;RX bytes:238029328 (227.0 MiB)  TX bytes:4768029 (4.5 MiB)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
